data.description: Welcome to your dream home in sought-after West End Manor! The well maintained residence boasts 4 bedrooms and 2.5 Baths, offering the perfect blend of comfort and Style. Nestled on a spacious lot, this property comes complete with an oversized detached garage, a versatile workshop, and expansive storage shed, providing ample space for all you needs. The Primary suite, complete with its private bath, ensures a tranquil retreat at the end of the day. New HVAC. Enjoy the benefits of prime location, schools, parks, shopping and dinning. Don't miss the opportunity to make this West End Manor gem your own!
